          p.home_page_section_subtitle Further information about our team and restaurant
      .row.justify-content-center.about_us_mobile_tab
        .col-lg-6.about_us_container
          h3.about_us_title Who We Are
          p.about_us_content(style="line-height: 1.8em")
            | In Downtown Moncton, Tandoori Zaika is serving authentic Indian vegetarian and non-vegetarian food. With more than 20 years of experience, we are offering a wide range of foods. Tandoori Zaika is dedicated to providing quality Indian Food. Our aim is to provide best service to our customers ensuring that Indian Dishes & Catering are always serves fresh which includes our Daily Buffet Specials as well.
            br
            br
            | As our name states Tandoori, Tandoori involves marinated meat being cooked over an intense fire in a tandoor, a clay oven. The meat is lowered into the oven on long metal skewers and cooked in this smoky and extremely hot environment until done.
            br
            br
            | The Tandoori Zaika specializes in creating a uniquely thoughtful atmosphere, which will not only excite one's tastes, but provide the perfect dining experience. We combine our own family recipes with style and personal flair to create a unique experience every time you visit us. We strive to make each visit satisfying and memorable.
          .read_more
            button.read_more_btn READ MORE
        .col-lg-5.about_section_photo
